RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', EoamPortResults.ContChkTxCount AS 'CC Tx Count', EoamPortResults.ContChkRxCount AS 'CC Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LoopbackTxCount AS 'LB Tx Count', EoamPortResults.AisTxCount AS 'AIS Tx Count', EoamPortResults.AisRxCount AS 'AIS Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LckTxCount AS 'LCK Tx Count', EoamPortResults.LckRxCount AS 'LCK Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LoopbackRxCount AS 'LB Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LinkTraceTxCount AS 'LT Tx Count', EoamPortResults.LinkTraceRxCount AS 'LT Rx Count', EoamPortResults.DelayMeasurementTxCount AS 'DM Tx Count', EoamPortResults.DelayMeasurementRxCount AS 'DM Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LossMeasurementTxCount AS 'LM Tx Count', EoamPortResults.LossMeasurementRxCount AS 'LM Rx Count', EoamPortResults.SlmTxCount AS 'SLM Tx Count', EoamPortResults.SlmRxCount AS 'SLM Rx Count', EoamPortResults.NumOfMegs AS '# MA/MEGs', EoamPortResults.NumOfMegEndPoints AS '# MEPs', EoamPortResults.DroppedPktCount AS 'Dropped Packet Count' FROM Port, EoamPortResults, EoamPortConfig WHERE ( EoamPortConfig.ParentHnd = Port.Handle AND EoamPortResults.ParentHnd = EoamPortConfig.Handle AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND EoamPortResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND EoamPortConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) UNION SELECT ExternalDevicePort.Name AS 'Port Name', EoamPortResults.ContChkTxCount AS 'CC Tx Count', EoamPortResults.ContChkRxCount AS 'CC Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LoopbackTxCount AS 'LB Tx Count', EoamPortResults.AisTxCount AS 'AIS Tx Count', EoamPortResults.AisRxCount AS 'AIS Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LckTxCount AS 'LCK Tx Count', EoamPortResults.LckRxCount AS 'LCK Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LoopbackRxCount AS 'LB Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LinkTraceTxCount AS 'LT Tx Count', EoamPortResults.LinkTraceRxCount AS 'LT Rx Count', EoamPortResults.DelayMeasurementTxCount AS 'DM Tx Count', EoamPortResults.DelayMeasurementRxCount AS 'DM Rx Count', EoamPortResults.LossMeasurementTxCount AS 'LM Tx Count', EoamPortResults.LossMeasurementRxCount AS 'LM Rx Count', EoamPortResults.NumOfMegs AS '# MA/MEGs', EoamPortResults.NumOfMegEndPoints AS '# MEPs', EoamPortResults.DroppedPktCount AS 'Dropped Packet Count' FROM ExternalDevicePort, EoamPortResults, Port, EoamPortConfig WHERE ( EoamPortConfig.ParentHnd = Port.Handle AND EoamPortResults.ParentHnd = EoamPortConfig.Handle AND ExternalDevicePort.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND EoamPortResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND EoamPortConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId )
